---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About | Justin Hoffmann">
  <section class="container">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <p>
      I'm a Systems Administrator with a passion for building reliable,
      secure, and efficient IT infrastructure. I enjoy solving technical
      problems, automating repetitive tasks, and continuously learning new
      technologies through both my professional work and my home lab.
    </p>

    <h2>Professional Experience</h2>

    <p>
      I currently work as a Systems Administrator at a Managed Service
      Provider (MSP), where I support a variety of business environments.
      My responsibilities include Microsoft 365 administration, Entra ID,
      Active Directory, endpoint management, cybersecurity, networking,
      and PowerShell automation.
    </p>

    <p>
      Every day I work with technologies including Microsoft 365,
      Microsoft Entra ID, Active Directory, PowerShell, NinjaOne,
      SentinelOne, Huntress, Guardz, Barracuda, and SonicWall to deploy,
      secure, monitor, and support client environments.
    </p>

    <h2>My Home Lab</h2>

    <p>
      Outside of work, I maintain a Proxmox-based home lab where I
      experiment with virtualization, Docker containers, networking,
      automation, and self-hosted services. My lab allows me to test new
      technologies, improve my troubleshooting skills, and build real-world
      projects that reinforce what I learn professionally.
    </p>

    <h2>Currently Learning</h2>

    <p>
      I'm continually expanding my knowledge of networking, Linux,
      automation, virtualization, and enterprise infrastructure. I'm
      currently focused on strengthening my networking expertise while
      continuing to build practical projects that demonstrate real-world
      problem solving.
    </p>

    <h2>Technologies I Use</h2>

    <div class="skills">
      <div>
        <h3>Microsoft</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Microsoft 365</li>
          <li>Microsoft Entra ID</li>
          <li>Active Directory</li>
          <li>PowerShell</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Endpoint Management</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>NinjaOne</li>
          <li>SentinelOne</li>
          <li>Huntress</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Guardz</li>
          <li>Barracuda</li>
          <li>SentinelOne</li>
          <li>Huntress</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Networking</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>SonicWall</li>
          <li>DNS</li>
          <li>DHCP</li>
          <li>VPN</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #cfcfcf;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .skills {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .skills h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .skills ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .skills li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #cfcfcf;
  }
</style>